            <div type="transcript" id="F582A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'm sorry for the Dead - Today -</l>
                    <l>It's such congenial times </l>
                    <l>Old neighbors have at fences - </l>
                    <l>It's time o'year for Hay, </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And Broad - Sunburned <app type="emendation"><lem>Ac - &lt;app type=&quot;division&quot;&gt;&lt;lem&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;/lem&gt;&lt;/app&gt;
 quaintance</lem><rdg>Acquaintance</rdg></app>
</l>
                    <l>Discourse between the Toil - </l>
                    <l>And laugh, a homely species </l>
                    <l>That makes the Fences smile - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It seems so straight to lie<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 away </l>
                    <l>From all the<add type="alternate" extent="noise">Sound</add>
 noise of Fields -</l>
                    <l>The Busy Carts - the fragrant<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Cocks - </l>
                    <l>The Mower's metre - Steals </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Trouble lest <app type="emendation"><lem>theyre</lem><rdg>they&#x27;re</rdg></app>
 homesick - </l>
                    <l>Those Farmers - and their Wives -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l><add type="alternate" extent="Set separate">Put</add>
Set separate from the Farming -</l>
                    <l>And all the Neighbor's lives - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A Wonder if the Sepulchre </l>
                    <l>Dont feel a lonesome way - </l>
                    <l>When Men - and Boys - and<add type="alternate" extent="Carts -">Larks -</add>
<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Carts - and June, </l>
                    <l>Go down the Fields to &quot;Hay&quot; -</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
